The exam committee allocates the supervision duties to the available teaching staff of the institute.
The care is taken that each faculty should not be allocated more than 5 duties.
The exam will have a start date and end date without any holidays in between except sundays. Faculty is not allocated duty in their own subjects.
A faculty is not allocated duty provided if it is not sick, not on duty leave and not the member of examination committee.
The duty is not allocated in both sessions on a day.
The suggested fields are as follows: Name, faculty type, subjectname, examdate, examday, session, subjectexam
The exam committee would like to know faculty wise list, date-wise faculty list, faculty on duty leave, faculty that are sick, faculty-wise supervision count
Write the java program to automate this scenario.